org.jruyi.me

Interface IRoute


  • public interface IRoute
    A route defines a rule for messages to be routed between two end points in one way.

    If a message is put into the message queue by end point from and its properties match the filter, then it will be routed to end point to.

    See Also:
    IRouteSet, IRoutingTable
